title: internal compiler error: encountered incremental compilation error with predicates_of(6fb04e5bc1990793-47e006422773ad5b)

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

labels.name: T-compiler
labels.description: Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

body:
I received the following error running cargo test. As requested in the output I'm reporting before I run cargo clean.

The commit hash / link for this code is here: https://github.com/chotchki/feophant/commit/558df4b0a8e9af24b6241cdc82446522af017295

(Please note the unit tests fail since I'm in the middle of test driven development of this code).
